@AiCvMatch.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5196

### Analyze CV against job description (replace path with your PDF)
POST {{AiCvMatch.Api_HostAddress}}/api/cv-match
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="jobDescription"

We are hiring a .NET developer with experience in ASP.NET Core, REST APIs, Entity Framework, and cloud deployment (Azure). Strong communication skills required.
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cvPdf"; filename="resume.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./resume.pdf
--boundary--
